the gift of love is a 1958 de luxe in cinemascope film directed by jean negulesco and starring lauren bacall and robert stack . the film 's screenplay was based on the short story " the little horse " by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; gardner white , originally published in a 1944 issue of good housekeeping , and previously made into the film sentimental journey ( 1946 ) , with john payne and maureen o'hara .